articles.author: Henry Foy, Felicia Schwartz
articles.title: Nato to develop $100bn Ukraine fund despite US concerns - Financial Times
articles.description: Alliance members agree to explore aid overhaul aiming to ‘Trump proof’ military support for Kyiv
articles.content: Nato is to start planning a $100bn military aid programme for Ukraine, according to the alliances head, despite the US urging caution over aspects of a proposal aiming to Trump proof western support.… [+3288 chars]
